honor of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Italy</ENAMEX>.") The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">commuters</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Rome</ENAMEX> reacted to those signs exactly as you
